          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0403P0_20030409_WH_16'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-patrick-mcloughlin' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0403P0_20030409_WH_16' title='Link to this speech by Mr Patrick McLoughlin' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-patrick-mcloughlin" title="Mr Patrick McLoughlin">Mr. McLoughlin</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I am grateful to the hon. Gentleman&#x2014;I was about to make that point. Wandsworth council's tax increase is 45 per cent., which translates into an increase of &#x00A3;181. However, in Islington council tax will rise by 21 per cent., an increase of &#x00A3;182. The hon. Gentleman is absolutely right: in 2003&#x2013;04, Wandsworth's council tax will be &#x00A3;584 whereas Islington's council tax will be &#x00A3;1,049.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0403P0_20030409_WH_17'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-curry' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
