            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_87wh' title='Col. 87WH &mdash; HC Deb 09 April 2003 vol 403 c87WH' name='column_87wh' href='#column_87wh' rel='bookmark'>87WH</a>
            demonstrably unfair. They recognise that, which is a major political problem for the Government. Norfolk, my own county council, has demonstrably lost out.</p><p>
